desc
@Optional values module.  This is the signature.
@


1.2
log
@Changed T to opt; new datatype option.
@
text
@(*  ==== OPTIONAL VALUES ====
 *          SIGNATURE
 *
 *  Copyright (C) 1992 Harlequin Ltd.
 *
 *  Description
 *  -----------
 *  This simple module provides a datatype which allows an object of type 'a
 *  to be optionally present.
 *
 *  Revision Log
 *  ------------
 *  $Log: option.sml,v $
 *  Revision 1.1  1992/01/03  15:30:45  richard
 *  Initial revision
 *
 *)


signature OPTION =
  sig

    datatype 'a opt =
      PRESENT of 'a
    | ABSENT

    datatype ('a,'b) option = 
      SOME1 of 'a
    | SOME2 of 'b

  end
@


